---
import DocsLayout from "../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-white">
    <section
      class="text-center mb-12 p-8 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-700/30 to-cyan-300/40 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <svg
          class="w-10 h-10 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
          ></path>
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white bg-linear-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text"
        >
          Tailwind CSS Configuration
        </h1>
      </div>

      <p class="text-body/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Learn how to configure and customize Tailwind CSS in your Astro project.
        From basic setup to advanced theming, master the configuration file.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-950/30 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">
          üí° <strong>Configuration File:</strong> All Tailwind customization happens
          in <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded"
            >tailwind.config.mjs</code
          > at the root of your project.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg
          class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Default Configuration
      </h2>

      <div
        class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default mb-6"
      >
        <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
          After running <code
            class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300"
            >npx astro add tailwind</code
          >, you'll get a basic config file:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-cyan-300 text-sm mb-2">tailwind.config.mjs</p>
          <pre
            class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: ['./src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,md,mdx,svelte,ts,tsx,vue}'],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/30"
      >
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Content Paths</h3>
        <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
          The <code class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-cyan-300"
            >content</code
          > array tells Tailwind where to look for class names:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
          <pre
            class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`content: [
  './src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,md,mdx,svelte,ts,tsx,vue}',
  './public/**/*.html',
],`}</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-yellow-950/30 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 rounded-lg"
        >
          <p class="text-yellow-200 text-sm">
            ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important:</strong> If Tailwind classes aren't working, make
            sure your file paths are included in the <code
              class="bg-black/30 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">content</code
            > array!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg
          class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Custom Breakpoints
      </h2>

      <div
        class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default"
      >
        <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
          Customize or extend the default responsive breakpoints:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
          <pre
            class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`export default {
  theme: {
    screens: {
      'xs': '475px',
      'sm': '640px',
      'md': '768px',
      'lg': '1024px',
      'xl': '1280px',
      '2xl': '1536px',
      '3xl': '1920px',
    },
  },
}`}</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-default">
                <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-cyan-400">Breakpoint</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-cyan-400">Min-width</th>
                <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-cyan-400">Usage</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-body/80">
              <tr class="border-b border-default/50">
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><code class="text-cyan-300">xs</code></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">475px</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"
                  ><code class="text-cyan-300">xs:text-lg</code></td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default/50">
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><code class="text-cyan-300">sm</code></td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4">640px</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"
                  ><code class="text-cyan-300">sm:flex</code></td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-default/50">
                <td class="py-3 px-4"><code class="text-cyan-300">3xl</code></td
                >
                <td class="py-3 px-4">1920px</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4"
                  ><code class="text-cyan-300">3xl:max-w-9xl</code></td
                >
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Plugins -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg
          class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Official Plugins
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div
          class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-3">
            @tailwindcss/typography
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Beautiful typography defaults for markdown content:
          </p>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-3">
            <p class="text-cyan-300 text-sm mb-2">Installation:</p>
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`npm install -D @tailwindcss/typography`}</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-3">
            <p class="text-cyan-300 text-sm mb-2">tailwind.config.mjs:</p>
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`export default {
  plugins: [
    require('@tailwindcss/typography'),
  ],
}`}</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-cyan-300 text-sm mb-2">Usage:</p>
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`<article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert">
  <h1>Markdown Content</h1>
  <p>Automatically styled!</p>
</article>`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Forms Plugin -->
        <div
          class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-3">
            @tailwindcss/forms
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Better default styles for form elements:
          </p>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-3">
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`npm install -D @tailwindcss/forms`}</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`export default {
  plugins: [
    require('@tailwindcss/forms'),
  ],
}`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-default"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-3">
            @tailwindcss/container-queries
          </h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
            Style elements based on parent container size:
          </p>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-3">
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`npm install -D @tailwindcss/container-queries`}</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <pre
              class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`<div class="@container">
  <div class="@lg:text-xl @2xl:text-2xl">
    Responsive to container, not viewport!
  </div>
</div>`}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg
          class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
        </svg>
        Complete Configuration Example
      </h2>

      <div
        class="bg-neutral-secondary-soft p-6 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/30"
      >
        <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">
          A production-ready Tailwind configuration with common customizations:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-black/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <pre
            class="text-sm text-cyan-200"><code>{`/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: ['./src/**/*.{astro,html,js,jsx,md,mdx,svelte,ts,tsx,vue}'],
  
  darkMode: 'class',
  
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        primary: {
          50: '#f0f9ff',
          500: '#0ea5e9',
          900: '#0c4a6e',
        },
        secondary: '#8b5cf6',
      },
      
      fontFamily: {
        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
        mono: ['Fira Code', 'monospace'],
      },
      
      fontSize: {
        'xxs': ['0.625rem', { lineHeight: '0.75rem' }],
      },
      
      spacing: {
        '18': '4.5rem',
        '128': '32rem',
      },
      
      animation: {
        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out',
        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.3s ease-out',
      },
      
      keyframes: {
        fadeIn: {
          '0%': { opacity: '0' },
          '100%': { opacity: '1' },
        },
        slideUp: {
          '0%': { transform: 'translateY(10px)', opacity: '0' },
          '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },
        },
      },
    },
  },
  
  plugins: [
    require('@tailwindcss/typography'),
    require('@tailwindcss/forms'),
  ],
}`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Best Practices -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg
          class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-400"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        Best Practices
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-950/30 to-emerald-950/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-500/20"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-400 mb-4">‚úì DO</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-body/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
              <span
                >Use <code class="bg-black/30 px-1 rounded text-xs">extend</code
                > to keep default utilities</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Use CSS variables for dynamic theming</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Keep custom values semantic and consistent</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Document your custom configuration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400">‚úì</span>
              <span>Use official plugins when available</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-950/30 to-pink-950/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-500/20"
        >
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-400 mb-4">‚úó DON'T</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-body/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">‚úó</span>
              <span>Override entire default theme</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">‚úó</span>
              <span>Add too many custom utilities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">‚úó</span>
              <span>Use arbitrary values everywhere</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">‚úó</span>
              <span>Forget to update content paths</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-red-400">‚úó</span>
              <span>Install unnecessary plugins</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Resources -->
    <section
      class="p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/40 to-blue-950/40 rounded-lg border border-cyan-500/30"
    >
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg
          class="w-8 h-8 text-cyan-400 flex-shrink-0"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Learn More</h3>
          <p class="text-body/80 mb-4">Explore more Tailwind topics:</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/docs/tailwind/dark-mode"
              class="px-4 py-2 bg-cyan-500 hover:bg-cyan-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors text-sm"
            >
              Dark Mode
            </a>
            <a
              href="/docs/tailwind/responsive"
              class="px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-tertiary hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors border border-default text-sm"
            >
              Responsive Design
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/configuration"
              target="_blank"
              class="px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-tertiary hover:bg-neutral-secondary-medium text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors border border-default text-sm"
            >
              Official Docs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
